Quote:  The diseases of the second group, usually termed "wilts" are due to the following organisms .. mattery-eye (a bacterial disease due to Phytomonas Solanaceara). Mattery-eye is expressed in an aggravated form, wilt of the whole plant being rapidly followed by its death.
